{"tid":384572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒病病人嘅世界係你地唔會明","createTime":"2017-09-02T12:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T15:03:29.000Z","uid":15389,"like":84,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab60186ce16ac93b3a5683383acc51a19e3035f","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"你地唔會明我地幾辛苦，日日都面對住滿腦子嘅負能量，一件好小事嘅事（就算我地都知係小事）都已經會牽動我地嘅情緒。我地會覺得自己無用，會覺得自己垃圾，但係我地都唔想㗎，我地都控制唔到自己唔好唔開心，相反，我地越想控制，越辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n我地會提自殺，可能唔止提一次。每個人面對唔到嘅關口都唔一樣，有啲人會因為學業，有啲人會因為愛情，你地唔明唔緊要，覺得我地無用都唔緊要，但請你：<br />\n<br />\n唔好指責我地「又用呢招」<br />\n唔好以為我地用死嚟威脅你地<br />\n唔好以為我地用呢樣野嚟搏同情<br />\n<br />\n每一次放棄了斷嘅念頭都要用好多好多勇氣，當中好多原因唔係因為我地唔敢死、唔想死，係我地有顧及到你地嘅感受，怕你地好傷心，所以寧願自己受返啲唔開心，寧願生無可戀，都唔去死。<br />\n<br />\n但聽到你地呢啲指責，我地會喺下次多一分諗法，會記得你地會笑我地/鬧我地又用呢招，既然你地唔信我地嘅決心，咁我地就實行畀你睇。<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊有患者，請唔好喺佢地唔開心嘅時候再鬧佢地，唔明真係唔重要，唔使講咩老生常談，話咩人生好美好呀之類，因為從我地越陷越深嘅當下，我地一早已經唔覺人生係美好。<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔好鬧，鬧我地自私，鬧我地唔上進，係你地唔知啲背後，我地已經用咗好大嘅努力，你地只見到我地唔開心嘅結果就去指責我地，公唔公平？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢講唔出佢咩事唔開心，請 唔 好 講 ：「都唔知你做乜。」呢句野真係好hurt，可能會令我地諗歪咗成為：我唔開心都係錯。 <br />\n<br />\n唔明真係唔緊要，陪住就夠。如果我地表現出好需要你，但唔開心時連野都同唔到你講，請畀我地一個擁抱，就已經好足夠，我地會好感激你嘅體諒同埋陪伴，多謝你地。"},{"pid":"f762a55ada0949517e818168c63bb3db96d9acf4","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c128448580a68a2a1ab7d02b96f7e03a0e3d74fa","tid":384572,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"根據去年發表的一份研究報告，約十分一的本地成人人口患有抑鬱症或混合性焦慮抑鬱障礙。現時抑鬱症的主流療法為藥物治療及心理治療，但部份患者不能適應服用抗抑鬱藥後的副作用，而廣泛使用心理治療又需要有充足數目的治療師，而且兩種療法對病情嚴重的患者未必能即時見效。因此，精神科醫生亦使用腦刺激療法來治療患者的抑鬱情緒。<br />\n第一種腦刺激療法是使用多年的腦電盪治療。不少臨床研究指出腦電盪治療可迅速改善抑鬱症患者病情，對病情嚴重、有自殺傾向的患者尤其適用。腦電盪治療是以電流通過患者腦部，造成身體抽搐。治療時患者需接受全身麻醉，並由麻醉科醫生緊密觀察。患者每隔三至四天接受治療一次，整個療程由兩、三次至十多次不等。<br />\n近年精神科醫生也開始使用其他種類的腦刺激療法，如重複經顱磁刺激及經顱直流電刺激。重複經顱磁刺激利用線圈產生電磁脈衝，在左腦前額葉表面位置造成電流，刺激腦部使其活動回復正常之餘，又不會造成抽搐，患者亦無需進行麻醉。患者一般需一星期接受治療五次，約四至六星期可完成整個療程。<br />\n較新的經顱直流電刺激，是通過貼在頭皮上的電極傳遞微弱電流（0.5-2毫安）至大腦表層。它不會造成抽搐，而是透過改變腦源性神經營養因子、大腦血液流和代謝等來改善情緒。最新的數據顯示它的療效可能和抗抑鬱藥及重複經顱磁刺激相若。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/200738_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F200738_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg&h=653ebb04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618f9dae33de27814b76980232e2040c7bac7118","tid":384572,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"I know thst feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇朋友"},{"pid":"3224516ea9d6b63dbc865c79501d8518b7c02e21","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據去年發表的一份研究報告，約十分一的本地成人人口患有抑鬱症或混合性焦慮抑鬱障礙。現時抑鬱症的主流療法為藥物治療及心理治療，但部份患者不能適應服用抗抑鬱藥後的副作用，而廣泛使用心理治療又需要有充足數目的治療師，而且兩種療法對病情嚴重的患者未必能即時見效。因此，精神科醫生亦使用腦刺激療法來治療患者的抑鬱情緒。<br />\n第一種腦刺激療法是使用多年的腦電盪治療。不少臨床研究指出腦電盪治療可迅速改善抑鬱症患者病情，對病情嚴重、有自殺傾向的患者尤其適用。腦電盪治療是以電流通過患者腦部，造成身體抽搐。治療時患者需接受全身麻醉，並由麻醉科醫生緊密觀察。患者每隔三至四天接受治療一次，整個療程由兩、三次至十多次不等。<br />\n近年精神科醫生也開始使用其他種類的腦刺激療法，如重複經顱磁刺激及經顱直流電刺激。重複經顱磁刺激利用線圈產生電磁脈衝，在左腦前額葉表面位置造成電流，刺激腦部使其活動回復正常之餘，又不會造成抽搐，患者亦無需進行麻醉。患者一般需一星期接受治療五次，約四至六星期可完成整個療程。<br />\n較新的經顱直流電刺激，是通過貼在頭皮上的電極傳遞微弱電流（0.5-2毫安）至大腦表層。它不會造成抽搐，而是透過改變腦源性神經營養因子、大腦血液流和代謝等來改善情緒。最新的數據顯示它的療效可能和抗抑鬱藥及重複經顱磁刺激相若。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/200738_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F200738_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg&h=653ebb04&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且兩種療法對病情嚴重的患者未必能即時見效。<br />\n<br />\n呢句係真，開頭睇完未有效果添，所以希望大家唔好再見我地睇得一次治療就就逼我地要即刻好返<br />\n<br />\n最hurt係：「你唔係睇醫生咩？點解仲係咁？」<br />\n<br />\n你感冒有時都未必睇一次醫生就好啦係咪？"},{"pid":"ba4c374846a630f37acccd8828d6e2a4a14450cd","tid":384572,"uid":139610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"世界太殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2cd7476942b1387cfb8640821832378564462d","tid":384572,"uid":129288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"好怕俾人知我嘅諗法 而家生存只係滿足佢地對我嘅期望"},{"pid":"25a75554d0fd0541a19730d3fa0db32388c152ce","tid":384572,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/202543_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F202543_8ce1c231ae9fb4e7dec3f5ed8880dd7a.jpg&h=a0369f90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d869b75063582c52823821fdda0ad10445a769fb","tid":384572,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b3316d9cdd036caeba7458856020662c87ffe0","tid":384572,"uid":11374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"有病好過冇病"},{"pid":"72059453cc4e4ca6e4f6ccb014f4e58f9f9e7974","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？"},{"pid":"643a17c67c4cca9562c8f914abc5c4dc56b0cc43","tid":384572,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401ed6b00eec222cf8165214bc3bb456ac3fcb6a","tid":384572,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32f7cb7e267606f527e54596237082b14acfad2","tid":384572,"uid":92494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"其實通過訓練係可以控制自己悲觀既念頭。"},{"pid":"37a48e333de65a49884085e1b7627a4d2b00a600","tid":384572,"uid":56858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9ad65c52576cc442e791473a39abda8fb5d035f","tid":384572,"uid":37153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"如果講到制止自殺呢個念頭要好大勇氣 咁高連登班經常叫春自稱想自殺既精神病人應該個個都係勇者"},{"pid":"2989a6483b6e50db2e40aaee137c547c7c698ea8","tid":384572,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"一樣有情緒病<br />\n會有時覺得全部人都唔明白自己"},{"pid":"d184a6905dcace9c89f550d2a341cebf00a3d81b","tid":384572,"uid":112850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我每日都好辛苦好想死"},{"pid":"4cf73464d01079267de258208ca137cb81a84da3","tid":384572,"uid":11261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"我都好想離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想父母傷心先未走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c0504b664e6dfc990979bd693a596ce74894af","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果講到制止自殺呢個念頭要好大勇氣 咁高連登班經常叫春自稱想自殺既精神病人應該個個都係勇者</blockquote><br />\n唔好拎叫春嗰啲嚟比啦⋯⋯<br />\n唔知點解釋你聽"},{"pid":"40f359789cd2bd2bbd43312e2a79db8ffa408c50","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實通過訓練係可以控制自己悲觀既念頭。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只能說我不是沒有努力過。"},{"pid":"c6018bcf66f507d513aef689cc978dfa82543fc7","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣有情緒病<br />\n會有時覺得全部人都唔明白自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經試過叫身邊嗰個睇有關抑鬱這回事本書<br />\n係拎埋本書畀埋佢睇<br />\n佢無細心睇<br />\n我都已經無再提起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452b76353ab29b3e4a8b660b8aa5c76e05556e0a","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我每日都好辛苦好想死</blockquote><br />\n告訴我 我陪你"},{"pid":"b1205a2b478653b4417b872b7bd5314d12731fc9","tid":384572,"uid":5466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeb2228c7080e62958824cc44309567a4288e20","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好想離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想父母傷心先未走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<br />\n我有時喊，爸媽會入嚟叫我唔好喊，同我講爸媽唔會離開<br />\n<br />\n爸媽係個好內斂嘅人，呢啲說話好難講出口，但佢地都會咁同我講<br />\n我唔敢話畀佢地聽我有呢個問題，亦都離開，我好怕佢地傷心"},{"pid":"c42f8a16116565df2b80f3d7c876df0b40fb1438","tid":384572,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地唔會明我地幾辛苦，<span style=\"color: red;\">日日都面對住滿腦子嘅負能量，一件好小事嘅事（就算我地都知係小事）都已經會牽動我地嘅情緒。</span>我地會覺得自己無用，會覺得自己垃圾，但係我地都唔想㗎，我地都控制唔到自己唔好唔開心，相反，我地越想控制，越辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n我地會提自殺，可能唔止提一次。每個人面對唔到嘅關口都唔一樣，有啲人會因為學業，有啲人會因為愛情，你地唔明唔緊要，覺得我地無用都唔緊要，但請你：<br />\n<br />\n唔好指責我地「又用呢招」<br />\n唔好以為我地用死嚟威脅你地<br />\n唔好以為我地用呢樣野嚟搏同情<br />\n<br />\n每一次放棄了斷嘅念頭都要用好多好多勇氣，當中好多原因唔係因為我地唔敢死、唔想死，係我地有顧及到你地嘅感受，怕你地好傷心，所以寧願自己受返啲唔開心，寧願生無可戀，都唔去死。<br />\n<br />\n但聽到你地呢啲指責，我地會喺下次多一分諗法，會記得你地會笑我地/鬧我地又用呢招，既然你地唔信我地嘅決心，咁我地就實行畀你睇。<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊有患者，請唔好喺佢地唔開心嘅時候再鬧佢地，唔明真係唔重要，唔使講咩老生常談，話咩人生好美好呀之類，因為從我地越陷越深嘅當下，我地一早已經唔覺人生係美好。<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔好鬧，鬧我地自私，鬧我地唔上進，係你地唔知啲背後，我地已經用咗好大嘅努力，你地只見到我地唔開心嘅結果就去指責我地，公唔公平？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢講唔出佢咩事唔開心，請 唔 好 講 ：「都唔知你做乜。」呢句野真係好hurt，可能會令我地諗歪咗成為：我唔開心都係錯。 <br />\n<br />\n唔明真係唔緊要，陪住就夠。如果我地表現出好需要你，但唔開心時連野都同唔到你講，請畀我地一個擁抱，就已經好足夠，我地會好感激你嘅體諒同埋陪伴，多謝你地。</blockquote><br />\n我都有呢個情況出現 成日自己諗埋一邊<br />\n又多負能量 但又會因為一件好小好小嘅事而開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cedcc72ff029250ee33a0026bc24bf8c61639a","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地唔會明我地幾辛苦，<span style=\"color: red;\">日日都面對住滿腦子嘅負能量，一件好小事嘅事（就算我地都知係小事）都已經會牽動我地嘅情緒。</span>我地會覺得自己無用，會覺得自己垃圾，但係我地都唔想㗎，我地都控制唔到自己唔好唔開心，相反，我地越想控制，越辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n我地會提自殺，可能唔止提一次。每個人面對唔到嘅關口都唔一樣，有啲人會因為學業，有啲人會因為愛情，你地唔明唔緊要，覺得我地無用都唔緊要，但請你：<br />\n<br />\n唔好指責我地「又用呢招」<br />\n唔好以為我地用死嚟威脅你地<br />\n唔好以為我地用呢樣野嚟搏同情<br />\n<br />\n每一次放棄了斷嘅念頭都要用好多好多勇氣，當中好多原因唔係因為我地唔敢死、唔想死，係我地有顧及到你地嘅感受，怕你地好傷心，所以寧願自己受返啲唔開心，寧願生無可戀，都唔去死。<br />\n<br />\n但聽到你地呢啲指責，我地會喺下次多一分諗法，會記得你地會笑我地/鬧我地又用呢招，既然你地唔信我地嘅決心，咁我地就實行畀你睇。<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊有患者，請唔好喺佢地唔開心嘅時候再鬧佢地，唔明真係唔重要，唔使講咩老生常談，話咩人生好美好呀之類，因為從我地越陷越深嘅當下，我地一早已經唔覺人生係美好。<br />\n<br />\n亦都唔好鬧，鬧我地自私，鬧我地唔上進，係你地唔知啲背後，我地已經用咗好大嘅努力，你地只見到我地唔開心嘅結果就去指責我地，公唔公平？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢講唔出佢咩事唔開心，請 唔 好 講 ：「都唔知你做乜。」呢句野真係好hurt，可能會令我地諗歪咗成為：我唔開心都係錯。 <br />\n<br />\n唔明真係唔緊要，陪住就夠。如果我地表現出好需要你，但唔開心時連野都同唔到你講，請畀我地一個擁抱，就已經好足夠，我地會好感激你嘅體諒同埋陪伴，多謝你地。</blockquote><br />\n我都有呢個情況出現 成日自己諗埋一邊<br />\n又多負能量 但又會因為一件好小好小嘅事而開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維持咗幾耐喇？"},{"pid":"03d60927f480b2e790ae3d61a8f22e6545147f77","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"話說我開post時打到差啲想喊<br />\n不過個個重要嘅人都係身邊，所以唔喊得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你地唔明，仲要講野傷害我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d74b4e9a9f13b3171c55141ac0361e55651ad3e","tid":384572,"uid":84369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"唔想死果part我都好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"01d2a24c89242a9ac1527f83492cfd711b2620dd","tid":384572,"uid":35668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地都有佢地既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff736e5ba79ccae2600fc3c96298ed992c9312b","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想死果part我都好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n 一直想被拉扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d3ea6701180dd735237741ff111344d15f1d9","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔想死果part我都好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n 一直都被拉扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"69fb906a34271ff4f13bd87d6c7b68291ebf5fa1","tid":384572,"uid":138833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知我係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日失眠 冇一兩個鐘都瞓到<br />\n瞓覺前會成個腦都係灰野/恐怖野<br />\n起碼有3 4日瞓前都會諗諗下喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對住人又會好正常 係獨處嘅時候先會極灰 覺得無人明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前試過想自殺<br />\n同埋試過自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依家無<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫唔叫有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇醫生"},{"pid":"a20253ac282113947e04d7d9c306084ae41f32b2","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地都有佢地既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地從來都無要求過啲咩，你地唔明真係唔緊要㗎，但可唔可以唔好咁樣傷害我地，陪住已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d771d7d5495b378ef96f5a5b6964b9580a28f0","tid":384572,"uid":138833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都唔知我係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日失眠 冇一兩個鐘都瞓<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>到<br />\n瞓覺前會成個腦都係灰野/恐怖野<br />\n起碼有3 4日瞓前都會諗諗下喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對住人又會好正常 係獨處嘅時候先會極灰 覺得無人明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前試過想自殺<br />\n同埋試過自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依家無<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫唔叫有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇醫生</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5e2c8cb054cf88794bbd7b28c6beadeee31b7fb8","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都唔知我係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日失眠 冇一兩個鐘都瞓到<br />\n瞓覺前會成個腦都係灰野/恐怖野<br />\n起碼有3 4日瞓前都會諗諗下喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對住人又會好正常 係獨處嘅時候先會極灰 覺得無人明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前試過想自殺<br />\n同埋試過自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依家無<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫唔叫有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無啲咩一直壓住你令你好大壓力？<br />\n有就試試去解決先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己已經去到無原因嘅地步<br />\n有原因嗰啲我都盡力去解決晒<br />\n<br />\n再唔掂要睇醫生呀/搵個社工傾一傾試下先都得"},{"pid":"82042c885569817b7f5713bf7b6e2adc5db1fa3c","tid":384572,"uid":4748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"明白你地既難處<br />\n不過有時你地都要體諒你地身邊既人既難處<br />\n<br />\n大家對事物既感受唔同<br />\n你唔明人地點解唔理解你地<br />\n人地都真係唔明點解你地會咁唔開心<br />\n所以唔好因為人地唔明你地既感受而發佢地脾氣...<br />\n<br />\n當然 無言既關心擁抱 隨時都可以奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"f478393b2ca913a3aff66c6b2658d5e76e91e678","tid":384572,"uid":36942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有抑鬱焦慮，唔開心咪唔開心，唔洗搞到全世界人陪自己唔開心。有d 人不停發放負能量，attention seeking，講負面說話，搞到抑鬱既好易俾人誤會放負能量同鬧。唔洗將所有野攬上身，唔開心就柄埋一面，每人都有難處。"},{"pid":"3d993d1e5130d040ab7f64c0a246ea55fb86b40a","tid":384572,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果講到制止自殺呢個念頭要好大勇氣 咁高連登班經常叫春自稱想自殺既精神病人應該個個都係勇者</blockquote><br />\n唔好拎叫春嗰啲嚟比啦⋯⋯<br />\n唔知點解釋你聽</blockquote><br />\n個d人都話自稱精神病架喎 有咩分別"},{"pid":"43ab4172f67f674b22454e746b6efd37c004a46b","tid":384572,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地都有佢地既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地從來都無要求過啲咩，你地唔明真係唔緊要㗎，但可唔可以唔好咁樣傷害我地，陪住已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過你煩到人，係人都有唔開心嘅事，但你係到小題大做喊苦喊忽煩到人㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n情緒病最鍾意屈人唔理解自己，噉你有冇去理解過普通人啊？事實係普通人唔會鍾人喊，負能量會傳染㗎嘛，你冇要求人，但你有騷擾到人你知唔知"},{"pid":"226eb3631a59691dd527f313548ccfb6e568f794","tid":384572,"uid":84369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想死果part我都好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n 一直都被拉扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n每日都有兩邊既自己嘈緊咁<br />\n<br />\n我從來無搵個朋友<br />\n就係驚煩到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a37d2e40f925f2818866f3c016a01f5f9eaef6a","tid":384572,"uid":52683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"我會嚴重到普通同學做小小野我就覺得佢係想串我或者其他負面野，我覺得已經無乜正能量出現係我人際關係入面，唔知有無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e37ed7d9b3d6f962bbc0869eeb7f963033284fd","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地都有佢地既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地從來都無要求過啲咩，你地唔明真係唔緊要㗎，但可唔可以唔好咁樣傷害我地，陪住已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過你煩到人，係人都有唔開心嘅事，但你係到小題大做喊苦喊忽煩到人㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n情緒病最鍾意屈人唔理解自己，噉你有冇去理解過普通人啊？事實係普通人唔會鍾人喊，負能量會傳染㗎嘛，你冇要求人，但你有騷擾到人你知唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地已經好努力收埋你地又知唔知？<br />\n就係知道會影響人 先一直死頂<br />\n但我地都會好努力想生活 想見最愛嘅人<br />\n有咩錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f1a8b9d5d7ac486710c191cf23129e954d50cd","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔想死果part我都好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n 一直都被拉扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n每日都有兩邊既自己嘈緊咁<br />\n<br />\n我從來無搵個朋友<br />\n就係驚煩到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朋友話 又用呢招呀？<br />\n我下次再有呢個諗法 一定會實行<br />\n唔會再顧人感受"},{"pid":"d77d69fd75a554b9ad361c0908a84cd1b2257444","tid":384572,"uid":5157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"75bf775d33dfb5fb37a9a849165a7268a140bbe2","tid":384572,"uid":138833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我都唔知我係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日失眠 冇一兩個鐘都瞓到<br />\n瞓覺前會成個腦都係灰野/恐怖野<br />\n起碼有3 4日瞓前都會諗諗下喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對住人又會好正常 係獨處嘅時候先會極灰 覺得無人明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前試過想自殺<br />\n同埋試過自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依家無<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫唔叫有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無啲咩一直壓住你令你好大壓力？<br />\n有就試試去解決先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己已經去到無原因嘅地步<br />\n有原因嗰啲我都盡力去解決晒<br />\n<br />\n再唔掂要睇醫生呀/搵個社工傾一傾試下先都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遇到少少事我都會好灰<br />\n可能因為細個屋企好多唔好嘅經歷加上缺乏愛 <br />\n同男朋友又嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴/絲打你都要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有冇睇開醫生/輔導？"},{"pid":"dce1a3990896e1855f0053594924737cb3aca997","tid":384572,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說我開post時打到差啲想喊<br />\n不過個個重要嘅人都係身邊，所以唔喊得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你地唔明，仲要講野傷害我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係因為重新先要俾佢知道你既感受嘛"},{"pid":"439e3231a4c9a97f83217a6c11a00dc8db973033","tid":384572,"uid":15389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我都唔知我係咪有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日失眠 冇一兩個鐘都瞓到<br />\n瞓覺前會成個腦都係灰野/恐怖野<br />\n起碼有3 4日瞓前都會諗諗下喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對住人又會好正常 係獨處嘅時候先會極灰 覺得無人明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前試過想自殺<br />\n同埋試過自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過依家無<br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫唔叫有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無啲咩一直壓住你令你好大壓力？<br />\n有就試試去解決先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己已經去到無原因嘅地步<br />\n有原因嗰啲我都盡力去解決晒<br />\n<br />\n再唔掂要睇醫生呀/搵個社工傾一傾試下先都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遇到少少事我都會好灰<br />\n可能因為細個屋企好多唔好嘅經歷加上缺乏愛 <br />\n同男朋友又嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴/絲打你都要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有冇睇開醫生/輔導？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5c45438f2b4c7952e249241a7bedfd4ee33fdc","tid":384572,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n每個人都有自己既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係點解好多人唔明我地嘅難處而又要指責我地？</blockquote><br />\n因為佢地都有佢地既難處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地從來都無要求過啲咩，你地唔明真係唔緊要㗎，但可唔可以唔好咁樣傷害我地，陪住已經好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過你煩到人，係人都有唔開心嘅事，但你係到小題大做喊苦喊忽煩到人㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n情緒病最鍾意屈人唔理解自己，噉你有冇去理解過普通人啊？事實係普通人唔會鍾人喊，負能量會傳染㗎嘛，你冇要求人，但你有騷擾到人你知唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地已經好努力收埋你地又知唔知？<br />\n就係知道會影響人 先一直死頂<br />\n但我地都會好努力想生活 想見最愛嘅人<br />\n有咩錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又或者咁樣講啦<br />\n你無錯係可以用人講<br />\n傾訴完之後心情係會好左既<br />\n因為最少會多左人明白你<br />\n<br />\n但同時間又咁樣講啦<br />\n每個人都有佢既事情要做<br />\n可能人地有時都會忙都會自己唔開心<br />\n又或者對方俾完意見你, 佢地會覺得可以解決到問題<br />\n但你無去做, 結果問題又出現<br />\n咁人地都會嬲你唔試下去做<br />\n<br />\n其實好多原因架<br />\n不過有情緒問題既人的確係好需要關心支持<br />\n我明白因為我女友都係咁樣<br />\n但耐性呢啲野總有一日會消耗<br />\n係消耗完之前<br />\n你最少都要俾你既朋友知道你所付出既努力<br />\n如果唔係佢地會覺得自己一直以來既口水都係白費<br />\n<br />\n多啲同人傾下溝通下啦<br />\n每日講少少<br />\n好過你積埋情緒爆發一發不可收拾"},{"pid":"8e0311507b80cfe12719daacbdbca8823aafd12e","tid":384572,"uid":102642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"曲奇 攬住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到樓主我發現有人明白我"}]}